Class ContainerNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.common.SourceLocation

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISourceLocation, IASNode, IContainerNode
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BlockNode, MetaTagsNode, TransparentContainerNode

    public class ContainerNode
extends TreeNode
implements IContainerNode
    ActionScript parse tree node representing a container. This is used to hold collections like function arguments and metadata attributes that don't come with a scope.
